      "content": "that looks like a good start but you cut off at the end. also, it feels a bit generic. can you actually finish the whole memo? and and seriously, make sure you don't miss any of those terms. the bot is really annoying, if it's missing even a few phrases like 'source of wealth' or 'adverse media' it'll just fail the whole thing. just make sure the text is packed with all those legal terms so it definitely hits the compliance threshold.",
